2026-07-14 09:21:33,663 INFO freight_fate.transcript: Parked at company yard: Phoenix Company Yard in the Phoenix service area, Arizona. Company driver with level 1, Yard Trainee. You have 5,567 dollars.  Career objective: Great Lakes Training Transport is looking for steady service, not perfection, with trainer notes still close by. Dispatch board. 1 of 15.
